MICROCOSM TECHNO said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 31.93% to NT$82,698,000 from NT$121,485,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales             82,698          121,485    
YOY%             -31.93%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            267,520          418,303    
YOY%             -36.05% 
